  "body":
    "\n### Clean ###\n# Binaries\n*.exe\n*.out\n\n# Project files\n*.prj\n\n# Directory used to store object files, abc files and assembly files\nClean System Files/\n\n# iTasks environment extra data\n*-data/\n*-www/\n*-sapl/\n",
