    "\n### Java ###\n# Compiled class file\n*.class\n\n# Log file\n*.log\n\n# BlueJ files\n*.ctxt\n\n# Mobile Tools for Java (J2ME)\n.mtj.tmp/\n\n# Package Files #\n*.jar\n*.war\n*.nar\n*.ear\n*.zip\n*.tar.gz\n*.rar\n\n# virtual machine crash logs, see http://www.java.com/en/download/help/error_hotspot.xml\nhs_err_pid*\nreplay_pid*\n",
