  "hash": "72eb04be3888ca304a4ddf4919b6025e4f1efb3dc178d588609a4de1fb573941",
  "body":
    "\n### TestComplete ###\n# Test Complete ignore files: https://support.smartbear.com/viewarticle/68002/\n\n# Tester-specific Settings\n*.tcCFGExtender\n*.tcLS\n\n# Type library declarations\n*.tlb\n\n# Log files\n*.tcLogs\n\n# Backup files\n*.bak\n",
